title: Hypixel Murder Mystery Stats Discord Bot
description: Developed a Python-based Discord server bot that provides detailed player statistics and enables comparisons across multiple players for the 'Murder Mystery' minigame genre on the Hypixel Minecraft server.

title: How Do Different Weather Conditions Affect NYC Subway Ridership?
description: Generated a detailed visualization that showcases the relationships between weather conditions such as rainfall and sunshine on NYC subway ridership using Altair.

title: Playlette: A Colour Palette Generator
description: Collaborated with a team of four to develop a software tool utilizing the Spotify API to generate a custom color palette based on the mood and song attributes of a user-provided Spotify playlist.

title: Recipe Complexity Analysis
description: Collaborated with a team member to analyze the impact of recipe complexity on recipe popularity on food.com as measured by the amount of user interactions in the form of ratings and reviews.
